      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement retry logic for transient errors and validate inputs to avoid synthesis failures."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimizing Performance with Kokoro Text to Speech"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Enhance performance by tuning request concurrency and leveraging caching for repeated phrases. Use asynchronous calls to minimize latency, and monitor metrics such as time-to-first-byte and error rates. For resource management, set timeouts and employ connection reuse in HTTP clients."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Advanced Deployment Strategies for Kokoro Text to Speech"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Scale horizontally by deploying Kokoro instances behind a load balancer in container orchestration platforms like Kubernetes. Integrate health checks and auto-scaling policies based on traffic patterns. Additionally, implement logging for audit trails and use distributed tracing to diagnose bottlenecks in multi-service architectures."
          }
        ]
      }
